    dc:description "Fig. 17. A–D. Bichoristes wareni McLean, 1992. A–B. Apical and apertural views, diameter 2.4 mm, stn DW4886 (MNHN). C. Protoconch of A. D. Protoconch of juvenile with thickened terminal lip, stn DW4893 (MNHN). E–G. Eudaronia?biconcava (Thiele, 1925), stn CP4913 (MNHN). E–F. Apertural and apical views, diameter 1.4 mm. G. Protoconch. Scale bars= 100 μm." ;
